content: I understand there is no support in wasmtime for 32 bit ARM, eg Raspberry Pi Model A ?
At this time, yes, Wasmtime doesn't support arm32. I don't know specifically much about the raspberry pi model you have though
Ok, that's fine. Its pretty old and should probably just be kept for posterity! This is what is has : http://cs107e.github.io/readings/arm1176.pdf
Scott Waye has marked this topic as resolved.
